So this is a command line to tool to help keep track of your pokemon's ev's.
It is not finished yet but is getting there. Can create a new pokemon, add ev's
to it, save, and load it again later. EV's are added by selecting a pokemon
you've defeated in battle. The program will automatically apply the appropriate
EV's to your pokemon.

** An example of the custom .pk save files **

NAME OF YOUR POKEMON ; HEALTH, ATTACK, DEFENSE, SP.ATTACK, SP.DEFENSE, SPEED

Bulby; 3,1,3,5,6,7
